{"tid":1602762,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓腹膜炎","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T01:11:46.000Z","uid":162841,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9b725524faf639bf756eb42230237a15ab57fc","tid":1602762,"uid":162841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻貓仔6個月大就中左乾性腹膜炎(已睇左兩個醫生同抽左血), 佢唔多食野越來越瘦又掉毛多，呢兩日開始精神差同隨地瀨尿，睇到好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲都有類似經驗？貓貓通常重有幾耐可以生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f1a8162a81327ce6d561639ea8bd226585feae","tid":1602762,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"點解無啦啦會中招有冇打齊針"},{"pid":"9cd258b7e60423aa435ec4e45646335f10dd34e4","tid":1602762,"uid":188672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"我知濕式依家有藥醫，不過好貴好貴（接近$20k，按貓咪重量計），仲要隻藥都未必100%醫得好<br />\n乾式要搵下有冇藥醫，因為我淨知濕式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df507558bcb3d106b315cac1f962f32f6552e8ef","tid":1602762,"uid":188672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd258b7e60423aa435ec4e45646335f10dd34e4","tid":1602762,"uid":188672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"我知濕式依家有藥醫，不過好貴好貴（接近$20k，按貓咪重量計），仲要隻藥都未必100%醫得好<br />\n乾式要搵下有冇藥醫，因為我淨知濕式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"好無助 點解會咁？長文慎入 黑店獸醫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/990619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/990619</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n可以睇下依個"},{"pid":"9f089cdf4011cbb817163fcfee04d0454693e289","tid":1602762,"uid":162841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f1a8162a81327ce6d561639ea8bd226585feae","tid":1602762,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"點解無啦啦會中招有冇打齊針"},"citedB